---------------------
SideWarp VERSIONS log
---------------------

1.1.0 (April 2026)
=====================
(added) Waveform visualization in ChuGL.
  - Visualizes the recorded waveform and the playhead position
  - Usage: SideWarp.inter() --> GGen;
  - See (_examples/mic.ck)
(added) SideWarp.max_speed
  - Set max playback rate - this was previously fixed to 1.0
(added) SideWarp.crossover_rate
  - Set the crossover_rate: Once the playback rate reaches crossover_rate
    the direction of the playback will change (i.e. from 0.5 to -0.5)
(added) SideWarp.scroll() and SideWarp.scroll(int scroll_state)
  - Set to 1 to enable scroll mode in the waveform, 0 to fix the waveform in space
(fixed) clicks and pops fixed

1.0.0 (December 2025)
=====================
(added) SideWarp effect initial release!
  - Sidechain the playback rate of your audio input